Package: GeoLink
Type: Package
Title: An R package for downloading, extracting and combining geospatial/remotely 
  sensed data with geocoded unit level data 
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Ifeanyi", "Edochie", email = "iedochie@worldbank.org", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Diana", "Jaganjac", email = "djaganjac@worldbank.org", role = c("aut")),
    person("Daylan", "Gomez", email = "dsalmerongomez@worldbank.org", role = c("aut"))
)
Description: A comprehensive toolkit for downloading and processing various types of 
    geospatial data. Supports multiple data sources including CHIRPS rainfall data, 
    night time lights, population data, elevation data, building footprints, CMIP6 
    climate model data, land use/land cover data, OpenStreetMap points of interest, 
    OpencellID cell tower data and electrification access data. Provides tools for 
    integrating this data with shapefiles and survey data for spatial analysis.
